{"tid":1249294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【召集大量連登仔】突襲! 分化藍絲 Fb反擊戰","createTime":"2019-06-21T16:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T17:00:05.000Z","uid":150778,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd82b9e507a2799650974b3eb77ebab7e1e5758","tid":1249294,"uid":150778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾一哥完全冇撚用個腦講野<br />\n分化唔到不得止<br />\n仲令前線狗軍心不穩 藍絲陷入互屌狀態<br />\n趁中共未有對策前<br />\n我地係時候用返中共常用招去反攻佢地<br />\n<br />\n第一波Fb page攻勢<br />\n首先大家要開個分身ac (可多於一個), 記得要有頭像, 同埋個人內容係唔可以比任何人見到, 如果唔係班老野會醒水發現<br />\n<br />\n我地要差不多時間係撐警fb page到留言炸鳩佢地, 同時互相like到上熱門留言, 另外見到其他質疑我地嘅留言時就等佢沉底, 唔需要特別覆<br />\n<br />\n有分身ac後，就要靠大家分批扮<br />\n1. 撐前線警犬人士<br />\n2. 撐一哥冇做錯嘅人<br />\n令佢地陷入和理非/勇武派網上內戰<br />\n對比起我地，班冇腦藍絲完全冇經驗應對<br />\n同時間我地要不斷煽風點火，將本身屌一哥嘅post/留言不斷讚好<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongPoliceForce%2F&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=a548ce58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongPoliceForce%2F&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=a548ce58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/</a><br />\n<br />\n係依家發動攻勢"},{"pid":"a0da0770f296b76c57a85241ed8e182bc88be9a1","tid":1249294,"uid":150778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:31:52.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"8c619357cb9ca010f38f09d7b2cb571e60582f9e","tid":1249294,"uid":150778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"大家有時間就幫手bookmark&amp;推"},{"pid":"7b77e9c2cad71528671c36834aff2372635e4089","tid":1249294,"uid":150778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"互like互推"},{"pid":"9ae1